snippet: Kei Nishikori ended Juan Martin del Potro's long winning run at the Swiss Indoors, edging their quarterfinal 7-5, 6-4 on Friday....
lead_paragraph: Kei Nishikori ended Juan Martin del Potro's long winning run at the Swiss Indoors, edging their quarterfinal 7-5, 6-4 on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Nishikori Ousts Del Potro in Swiss Indoors Quarterfinals
headline.main: Nishikori Ousts Del Potro in Swiss Indoors Quarterfinals
